      <title>研究表明北美电网停电风险正在上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/blackout-risk-is-rising-for-north-american-grids-study-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据电网可靠性监管机构的报告，由于电力需求激增和化石燃料发电厂的关闭，未来十年北美大部分地区停电风险将增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/blackout-risk-is-rising-for-north-american-grids-study-says</guid>
